text: Þis is ðæt land gemære to scepwæsce tune.
Ærest on sture to læcce pole, & of læcce pole ondlong þæs sices ongean stream þæt hit cymeð to þam hale.
And from þam hale þæt hit cymð to þam sealtpytte to hwætdune.
And of hwætdune to torde lande.
And of torde londa up on cyric hyll.
Of cyric hylle to stan hylle, & of stan hylle to þam hæðenan byrig gelse.
